headline: NetApp Hosts Technology Sessions at 2025 INSIGHT Conference in Las Vegas, Nevada
summary: SUNNYVALE, Calif., October 07, 2025--NetApp (NASDAQ: NTAP) will hold their 2025 INSIGHT™ customer conference in Las Vegas, Nevada on October 14–16, 2025.

headline: Research Finds Data Readiness and Infrastructure as Critical to Success in the AI Era
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., October 07, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today unveiled a new global Enterprise AI maturity study conducted by IDC*.
